<li id="cite_note-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4" title="">^</a></b> The sources frequently say that, in his youth, he was called by the nickname "Al-Amin" meaning "Honest, Truthful" cf. Ernst (2004), p. 85.</li>
<li id="cite_note-Goldman-5"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Goldman_5-0" title="">^</a></b> Elizabeth Goldman (1995), p. 63</li>
